ended.labl: End of Civil War. Coded “1” if civil war ends during country year, “0” if ongoing, Missing(.) otherwise.

waryrs.labl: Number of War Years for each onset

mtnest.labl: Percent Mountainous Terrain. Based on work by geographer A.J. Gerard for the World Bank’s “Economics of Civil War, Crime, and Violence” project.

cowwars.labl: Number of Civil Wars in progress using the Correlates of War (COW) coding.

lpopl1.labl: Log of population lagged one year, with 0 for start of country series.

ethfrac.labl: Ethnic-linguistic fractionalization based on the Atlas Marodov Mira.

ncontig.labl: Noncontiguous State. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if a country is a noncontinuous state, “0” otherwise.

colwars.labl: Number of Civil Wars in progress using Collier and Hoeffler’s coding.

cowonset.labl: Civil War Onset using the Correlates of War (COW) coding. Coded “1” if onset in current year, “0” otherwise.

war.labl: Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if war ongoing during country year, “0” otherwise.

polity2.labl: Polity is the difference between Polity IV’s measure of democracy minus its measure of autocracy. Values range from –10 to 10.

colonset.labl: Civil War Onset using Collier and Hoeffler’s coding. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if onset in current year, “0” otherwise.

wars.labl: Number of wars in progress during a given country year

sdwarl.labl: War in last period using Doyle and Sambanis. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if Doyle and Sambanis war ongoing in last period, “0” otherwise.

nwstate.labl: New State. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if state is in its first two years of existence, “0” otherwise.

warl.labl: WAR lagged one year, with 0 for start of country series.

sdonset.labl: Civil War Onset using Doyle and Sambanis’s coding. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if onset in current year, “0” otherwise.

gdpenl.labl: GDPEN lagged one year, with 0 for start of country series.

colbrit.labl: Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if country was a former British colony, “0” otherwise.

sdwars.labl: Number of Civil Wars in progress using Doyle and Sambanis’s coding.

deml.labl: Lagged Democracy. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if polity2l > 5, “0” otherwise.

cowwarl.labl: War in last period using Correlates of War (COW) coding. Coded “1” if COW war ongoing in last period.

colwarl.labl: War in last period using Collier and Hoeffler’s coding. Dichotomous variable. Coded “1” if Collier and Hoeffler war ongoing in last period, “0” otherwise.

instab.labl: Instablitiy. Greater than 2 change in Polity2 measure in last 3 years.
